Package: regexcite
Title: Tools for Splitting Strings with Regular Expressions.
Version: 0.0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Juanita", "Rodríguez", , "y.rodrigu@uni-muenster.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:  Provides a simple utility for splitting character strings using
    regular expressions. The package demonstrates the basic structure of an R
    package and includes functions for extracting and manipulating text
    components based on user-defined delimiters. It was developed as part of
    the R Packages (2nd edition) "Whole Game" tutorial.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
